Purchase STEP 5 to obtain the Big Three's Perfect Mold Selection Box for a guaranteed SSR!

1. Step Up Package
- Step Up Packages must be purchased in sequential order. If you want to buy a higher-level Step Up Package, you will need to buy the packages for the previous levels first.
- E.g. To buy Step 2 Package, you must first buy Step 1 Package, and so on.

2. SSR Guaranteed Manufacturer Mold Selection Box in Step 5 Package
- SSR Guaranteed Manufacturer Mold Selection Box contains Perfect Molds from Elysion, Missilis Industry, and Tetra Line.
- Select and obtain 1 Manufacturer Perfect Mold.

3. Manufacturer Perfect Mold
- Collect a certain amount of molds to recruit an SSR Nikke from a specific manufacturer.
- This excludes certain Nikkes, such as limited Nikkes and Nikkes in Liberation.
- The probabilities of recruiting each Nikkes in one mold are the same.
- Each Manufacturer Perfect Molds will have the following Nikkes available. This will not be subject to revision in the future.

Elysion
Emma, Privaty, Signal, Poli, Miranda, Brid, Soline, Diesel, Vesti, Eunhwa, Guillotine, Maiden, D, Helm

Missilis
Maxwell, Yuni, Liter, Julia, Centi, Drake, Crow, Pepper, Admi, Epinel, Jackal, Laplace

Tetra
Sugar, Exia, Alice, Frima, Mary, Milk, Yulha, Ludmilla, Rupee, Yan, Dolla, Novel, Folkwang, Sakura, Viper, Cocoa, Soda, Biscuit, Aria, Noise, Volume

Purchase STEP 5 to obtain 40 Advanced Recruit Vouchers!
Purchase all the STEPs to obtain Advanced Recruit Vouchers and various items!

What are Step Up Packages?
- Step Up Packages consist of several smaller Step Packages that you purchase in sequential order. If a Step Package catches your eye, you will need to purchase the previous Step Package first to be able to purchase it.
- For example: If you wish to purchase the STEP 2 Package, you must first purchase the STEP 1 Package.
